      <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#f5f0e8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin:0 0 8px 0;">The Supplements Didn't Work</p>
      <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:13.5px;color:#999;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">You've tried zinc. D3. Ashwagandha. TestoPrime. Nugenix. The cabinet is full. The results are empty.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background:#141414;border:1px solid #2a2a2a;border-top:2px solid #C9A84C;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 20px;">
