      <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#f5f0e8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin:0 0 8px 0;">She Sees It. She Hasn't Said It.</p>
      <p style="font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-size:13.5px;color:#999;line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Your wife hasn't brought it up. But you catch the look. The quiet disappointment.</p>
